{"hash":"135b09247c7a2fd5b6f9c4f9308e3a6e4c2d68c5","data":{"weekSchedule":{"id":"00b729f0c41171fdc156332dbb2c4256","title":"Flexbox and Media Queries","excerpt":"The backbone of responsive design","week":3,"content":"<h2 id=\"week-31\"><a href=\"#week-31\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Week 3.1</h2>\n<h3 id=\"flexbox\"><a href=\"#flexbox\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Flexbox</h3>\n<p>Flexbox is the new way to create layouts on HTML. No more floats!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1N0ZPUPeT5vbozh4skcPCjyKBQEpLxE3hZhZYpXMFw1E/edit?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Slides - Flexbox</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"pre-class-readings\"><a href=\"#pre-class-readings\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Pre-Class Readings</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">CSS Tricks Guide to Flexbox</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/CSS/CSS_layout/Flexbox\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">MDN Guide to Flexbox</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://codepen.io/enxaneta/full/adLPwv\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Flexbox Playground</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://flexboxfroggy.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Flexbox Froggy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.flexboxdefense.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Flexbox defense</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://css-tricks.com/the-peculiar-magic-of-flexbox-and-auto-margins/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Flexbox and margins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/JJSoEo8JSnc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">CSS in 20 mins (Video)</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"week-32\"><a href=\"#week-32\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon ic